channel.title: Nulls
channel.description:
Im getting ran out by nulls.. I had this once before, but the base was pimp, so i figured it was outdated and couldn't handle silab's items. Well, why does it do it now? It says all players on are nulls, and no one else can get on because of this.
Nulls are shitty smelly creatures.

item.dc:creator: @Java_Is_My_Bitch Java Is My Bitch™
item.description:
@Java_Is_My_Bitch wrote:

Boo all of you.

First of all your compiler is gay, get the fuck rid of it. Put all java files in a folder called java and all class files in a folder called class. Then use this compiler:

@echo off
javac -g:none -nowarn -d ./Class/ ./Java/*.java
pause

Then when you compile you will get an error, if i’m correct, its something to do with an unclosed literal. All other compilers fail.
